channel.title: WhiteScape
channel.description:
Most of you probably know i've left the community for couple of weeks to decide what i actually wanted to do with WhiteScape, and after many requests of many people i've chosen to return.
I arrived back in my forum, and tried to go to my forum with www.whitescape.net, now it seems to be Tasty Noob bought the domain from Kevin (who did leak my sources some time ago !) for a stupid level 100 runescape account... so i have no more domain left, and Kevin is not taking action against Tasty Noob, so there is no other choice then banning both, also XerozCheez is banned from my forum for leaking magic to code Phate.
also Tasty Noob is claiming he made WhiteScape, and just stolen it or something like that, but this is one big lie... like other pople already told: he's name tells alot about him (mostly the last part)
you cna always reach my development forum at: [url=http://whitefang-wf.no-ip.org/whitescape/forum/index.php]http://whitefang-wf.no-ip.org/whitescape/forum/index.php[/url]
Greets, WhiteFang
